      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a pretty intense way to put it. So u think it's mostly just a tactic people use to shut down debate? Like, is \"fake news\" even a real thing where news is actually being made up, or is it just a label used to ignore stuff people don't like?",
